V0102_01_00_00_0.text:
I don't need your respect.
All I need is victory!

V0102_01_00_01_0.text: By combining my Cyber Legacy with the Underworld Deck, you don't stand a chance!

V0102_01_00_02_0.text: Jaden, you once proved to be an exemplary challenger.

V0102_01_00_02_1.text: Let's see if you still are!

V0102_01_00_05_0.text:
Aster...
No matter who I Duel, it will still end in my victory!

V0102_01_00_07_0.text: My Cyber Legacy versus your Crystal Beasts.

V0102_01_00_07_1.text: Let's see which one's truly the most powerful.

V0102_01_00_09_0.text: Yubel is the strongest monster spirit in existence.

V0102_01_00_09_1.text: If this is the last Duel I ever take part in, I’m going to enjoy every last move.

V0102_01_00_10_0.text: You actually think you can defeat me?

V0102_03_00_00_0.text: I don't think you can survive until the end!

V0102_03_00_05_0.text: I will steal victory from you!

V0102_05_00_00_0.text: With this, I shall be victorious!

V0102_06_01_01_0.text: Nice move, but here's a better one!

V0102_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Different Dimension Capsule!

V0102_08_00_01_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0102_08_00_03_0.text: This is the ultimate Fusion card!

V0102_08_00_03_1.text: I activate my Spell, Power Bond!

V0102_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Attack Reflector Unit!

V0102_08_00_04_1.text: Cyber Dragon evolves into Cyber Barrier Dragon!

V0102_08_00_05_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Photon Generator Unit!

V0102_08_00_05_1.text: I tribute Cyber Dragon to Special Summon Cyber Laser Dragon!

V0102_08_00_06_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Return Soul!

V0102_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Future Fusion!

V0102_08_00_08_0.text:
My Counter Trap activates!
Damage Polarizer!

V0102_08_00_10_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Cyberdark Impact!!

V0102_08_00_11_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Evolution Burst!

V0102_08_00_12_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Overload Fusion!

V0102_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Cyber Shadow Gardna!

V0102_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Cybernetic Zone!

V0102_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Cybernetic Hidden Technology!

V0102_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Cybernetic Fusion Support!

V0102_08_00_17_0.text:
I don't think so!
I activate my Counter Trap!
Trap Jammer!

V0102_08_00_18_1.text: I send cards in my Deck to the Graveyard to drop the battle damage to 0!

V0102_08_00_19_0.text:
I knew you'd try that.
So I had a Counter Trap ready!
Fusion Guard!

V0102_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Rare Metalmorph!

V0102_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Megamorph!

V0102_08_00_22_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Creature Swap!

V0102_08_00_23_0.text:
Your timing's all off.
I play my Quick-Play Spell, Battle Fusion!

V0102_08_00_24_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Monster Reborn!

V0102_08_00_25_0.text:
Witness my Quick-Play Spell!
Dimension Explosion!

V0102_08_00_26_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Ruthless Denial!

V0102_08_00_27_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Fusion Recovery!

V0102_08_00_28_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Cyber Network!

V0102_08_00_29_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Cyber Repair Plant!

V0102_08_00_30_0.text:
I reveal my Trap Card!
Metalmorph!

V0102_09_00_01_0.text: Cyber Laser Dragon, activate your effect!

V0102_09_00_26_0.text: The Light - Hex-Sealed Fusion's effect activates!

V0102_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0102_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0102_13_00_02_0.text:
Heh heh heh...
It's over for you!
Come, Cyber End Dragon!

V0102_13_00_03_0.text:
Check this out!
Cyber Barrier Dragon!

V0102_13_00_09_0.text: Meet the last monster you'll ever see!

V0102_13_00_10_0.text:
It's over for you! 
Chimeratech Fortress Dragon!

V0102_13_00_12_0.text: I Special Summon a Level 10 Cyber!

V0102_13_00_16_0.text:
This is just what I need!
Metallizing Parasite - Lunatite!

V0102_13_00_17_0.text: Exploder Dragon bursts on the scene!

V0102_13_00_22_0.text: I banish Cyber End Dragon from my Extra Deck!

V0102_13_00_22_1.text:
Come forth!
Malefic Cyber End Dragon!

V0102_13_00_30_0.text: Toon Cyber Dragon's bringing the charm!

V0102_13_00_32_0.text: Perfect! I play Metallizing Parasite - Soltite!

V0102_13_00_33_0.text: Good! I play The Light - Hex-Sealed Fusion!

V0102_19_00_06_0.text:
Cyber Phoenix!
Set the world aflame!

V0102_19_00_08_0.text:
Feel the full might of my ancient birthright - the Cyber Legacy!
Attack, Cyberdark Dragon!

V0102_19_00_14_0.text:
You want me to bring it on? Well, consider it brought!
Chimeratech Fortress Dragon! Attack!

V0102_19_00_16_0.text:
Here I go!
Cyber Eltanin attacks!

V0102_19_00_34_0.text: Toon Cyber Dragon, show 'em this is no laughing matter!

V0102_19_00_36_0.text: I attack with Metallizing Parasite - Soltite!

V0102_28_00_01_0.text: To reach the top of the world and achieve even greater victories...

V0102_28_00_01_1.text: I'm willing to get rid of my old friend, Cyber End Dragon!

V0102_28_00_02_0.text: All that matters in life is victory!

V0102_28_00_02_1.text: You may know how to Duel, but you don't know how to win!

V0102_28_00_10_1.text: It’s unfortunate you aren’t going to be around to witness it, Yubel!

V0102_28_00_11_0.text: The Zane you knew is long gone and he’s never coming back!

V0102_28_00_11_1.text: And nothing you say can change my mind!

V0102_29_00_01_0.text: Argh... I don't need your pity!

V0102_29_00_02_0.text:
Looking back, I realize I had all the glory...
But I missed out on having any of the fun.

V0102_29_00_03_0.text:
Jaden, you'll be the top student at this school.
Despite your grades.

V0102_29_00_09_0.text: You're not so bad of a prof, Dr. Crowler.

V0102_29_00_10_0.text: I've dueled all over this crazy world...

V0102_29_00_10_1.text:
To find my moment to shine...
And I think I finally did... In my final moments...

V0102_29_00_11_1.text:
When did you become a greater Duelist than me?
I'm proud of you.

V0102_30_00_02_0.text: It'll be nice if you end your turn sometime this century.

V0102_33_00_00_0.text: This is the power of my Cyber Legacy!

V0102_34_00_02_0.text: Any pain you inflict only serves to remind me how much I yearned for a fight!

V0102_34_00_03_0.text: Bring it on! More! Fire me up!

V0102_34_00_04_0.text: Respecting your opponent is absolutely pointless. Because only victors deserve respect!

V0102_34_00_05_0.text:
Ergh...
How much more can my heart handle...

V0102_34_00_06_0.text: This Duel isn't for fun and games. You ready?

V0102_34_00_07_0.text:
I didn't come here to chat. 
I came to fight.

V0102_34_00_08_0.text: With my Cyber Legacy, my power knows no bounds!

V0102_34_00_09_0.text: No... I don't want to lose!
